---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home | Jvke's Blog">
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-20 text-center">
    <div class="avatar placeholder mb-6">
      <div class="bg-ctp-surface0 text-ctp-mauve rounded-full w-24 border-4 border-ctp-mauve shadow-lg">
        <span class="text-3xl font-bold">JT</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-6xl mb-4">테스트!</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-ctp-subtext0 mb-8 max-w-md">
      노션은 싫고, Next.js는 무거워서 직접 만든 <br/>
      <strong>Astro + Catppuccin</strong> 블로그입니다.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-primary">글 보러가기</a>
      <button class="btn btn-outline border-ctp-pink text-ctp-pink hover:bg-ctp-pink hover:border-ctp-pink">Github</button>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>